<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> willig, <expan>und<ex>er</ex>tenig</expan>
                        dienst sein <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>mechtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> allczeit voran bereyt.
                                <expan>Hochgeborn<ex>er,</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu eren zwey <expan>bancz<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        bey uns machen <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, die wir dem
                                <expan>Melmeist<ex>er</ex></expan> gen Ofen geschikt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> die von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>zu <expan>antwurte<ex>n</ex></expan> und</add> von uns zu
                                <expan>schenk<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ir das in gut von uns
                                <expan>aufneme<ex>n</ex></expan> wellet und uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> hinfür lasset
                            <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, als ir bisher
                                <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> getan habt. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> allczeit
                                <expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Viti. </ab>
